SYNOPSIS
========
   int valid_query_snoop(objectÂ ob)

DESCRIPTION
===========
   Should return 1 if `previous_object()` (the one that called query_snoop(E) 
   is allowed to query whether ob is being snooped, 0 if not.

   The master object is always allowed to use query_snoop(E).

SEE ALSO
========
   valid_snoop(M), query_snoop(E), snoop(E)
